# {{PROJECT_NAME}} — SOC 2 Controls Mapping

> **This is a starting-point template, not audit advice and not legal advice.**
> A SOC 2 audit measures actual operating effectiveness over the audit period;
> documenting controls is necessary but not sufficient. Engage a CPA
> firm experienced with SOC 2 audits to scope and execute the audit.

